{
  "texts": [
    "However, RT-PCR has some drawbacks.",
    "The RT-PCR test is a timeconsuming procedure [4].",
    "Patients who have the device placed deep within their noses or mouths must also endure severe treatment [5].Other methods can be employed, including computed tomography (CT Scan) and Chest X-ray (CXR) imaging.",
    "When comparing CT Scan to CXR, CT Scan is timeconsuming, expensive, less accurate and subjects patients to greater risks.",
    "Chest radiograph, on the other hand, is available in the majority of hospitals and clinics, making it more widely accessible [6]."
  ]
}